            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01DHg1DZM3DzxCnL2WsT4o5R\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary of my findings:\\n\\n## CONFIRMED\\n\\nThe landing page is **properly instrumented** with L10.createLead() for lead capture. Here's what I verified:\\n\\n### ✅ Components with Lead Capture Forms:\\n\\n1. **Hero Component** (`/src/components/Hero.tsx`)\\n   - ✅ Imports `L10` from `@/lib/tracking`\\n   - ✅ Uses `await L10.createLead(email)` on form submission\\n   - ✅ Proper error handling with try/catch\\n   - ✅ Shows success state after lead creation\\n   - ✅ Displays error messages to users\\n\\n2. **FinalCTA Component** (`/src/components/FinalCTA.tsx`)\\n   - ✅ Imports `L10` from `@/lib/tracking`\\n   - ✅ Uses `await L10.createLead(email)` on form submission\\n   - ✅ Proper error handling with try/catch\\n   - ✅ Shows success state after lead creation\\n   - ✅ Displays error messages to users\\n\\n### ✅ Tracking Library:\\n\\nThe `/src/lib/tracking.ts` file is properly configured with:\\n- ✅ `L10.createLead()` function that handles both API submission and Google Ads conversion tracking\\n- ✅ Automatic visitor and visit token generation\\n- ✅ UTM parameter tracking\\n- ✅ GCLID tracking for Google Ads\\n- ✅ Proper error handling with custom `LeadError` class\\n- ✅ Environment variable configuration (VITE_API_BASE_URL, VITE_SIGNUP_TOKEN, VITE_GOOGLE_ADS_SEND_TO)\\n\\n### ✅ Other Components Verified (No Forms):\\n\\n- Header - Only has navigation and CTA button (scrolls to signup)\\n- Features - Static feature list\\n- Problem - Static pain points\\n- HowItWorks - Static process steps\\n- SocialProof - Static testimonials and stats\\n- Footer - Static footer content\\n\\n**Status: CONFIRMED** - All lead capture forms are properly instrumented with L10.createLead().\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":727,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":23711,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":727,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":524,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
